<title>Hint</title>
<para id="fs-id1167794138240">Change the depth function, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> and the limits of integration.</para>
</commentary>
</exercise>
</note>
